<li class='cover' id='bookCover_672044'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/672044.Grass_on_the_Wayside"><img alt="Grass on the Wayside" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1190924550l/672044.jpg" />
